title: Classic Soul Power! Collection II [.MP3@192kbs]
description:
Title: Classic Soul Power! Collection II

Sequel to Classic Soul Power Collection compilation of soul styles and artists from the 60's & 70's! Nearly 100 more classic R&B and Soul
favorites. A total of 4 extra full CDs of music! Second in the Classic Soul Power Collection series. Easy listening 
R&B Billboard charts hits. Northern Soul, Chicago Soul, Philly Soul, West Coast Soul, New Orleans Soul, 
Detroit Soul, Memphis Soul & Psychedelic Soul. Format: [.mp3] @ 192Kb/s. Enjoy! 

Genre: R&B/Soul/Funk/Pop/Ska/Blues
